posting_body: ['Lofts at Farmers Market', 'Featured Floorplan: 1-bed / 1-bath / 847 sq ft', 'Monthly Rent: $1810', 'Deposit: Call', 'show contact info', 'Description: Life can get busy and stressful, and this is precisely why the place that you call home is so important.', 'When you have a quiet, safe, and beautiful place to put your feet up at the end of a long day, it makes facing tomorrow that much easier.', 'The Lofts at Farmers Market strives to create a peaceful oasis in the heart of Saint Paul, Minnesota where you can relax, refresh, and rejuvenate.', 'Lease Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month, 16-Month', 'Pet Policy: Dogs and cats welcome: Max. 2 allowed per home, deposit $200, one-time fee $200, monthly rent $40.', 'No weight limit, breed restrictions apply.', 'Apartment Amenities:', '❖ Baseball Field and Farmers Market Views', '❖ Big Windows', '❖ Dishwasher', '❖ Double Pane Windows', '❖ Granite Countertops', '❖ High Ceilings', '❖ High Speed Internet Access', '❖ Microwave', '❖ Smoke Free Community', '❖ Stainless Steel Energy Efficient Appliances', 'Community Features:', '❖ Accepts Electronic Payments', '❖ Barbecue/Grill', '❖ BBQ Grill', '❖ Bicycle Storage', '❖ Coffee Bar', '❖ Elevator', '❖ Fitness Center', '❖ Free Weights', '❖ Property Manager on Site', '❖ Public Transportation', '❖ 24 Hour Availability', '❖ 24-Hour Fitness Center', '❖ Barbecue/Grill Area', '❖ Bike Repair Stations', '❖ Community-Wide WiFi', '❖ Controlled Access Building', '❖ Dry Cleaning Service Available', '❖ Pet Washing Station', '❖ Property Manager on Site', '❖ Reservable Clubhouse', 'Call us:', 'show contact info', '260 5th St E', 'St. Paul, MN 55101', 'Tue - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Please note pricing and availability subject to change.', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '91F292BECB024B']
